Just something I made for our Deathmatch server around Christmas time last year. Never got around to uploading it anywhere.

Not sure who made the original crackhouse, but credits to them for making a cool deathmatch map. Only things I did to it was add the snow on the ground, falling snow, christmas tree, snowman, and removed the hostages. (For infinate playtime on deathmatch servers)
